    },
    {
      "id": "5dce31beaff09e000033f044",
      "text": "[時代遅れで動きの遅い「会社支給のPC」は、年間19日分の仕事時間を奪っている｜WIRED.jp https://wired.jp/2017/03/23/productivity-old-computer/]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1573794238,
      "updated": 1573794240
    },
    {
      "id": "5dce31c0aff09e000033f045",
